## ğŸ“Š Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

- Overall churn rate: **26.5%**
- Monthly contract customers churn more than long-term
- Churn highly correlated with:
  - Contract Type
  - Customer Service Calls
  - Electronic Billing
  - Tenure & Internet Service Type

